measure: state employees who had contact with an infected person must self quarantine
public offices and counters are closed
events with more than 50 persons are banned
day care centers are closed with some exceptions
moving houses is permitted but distancing and hygiene have to be ensured
municipal offices and counters are closed to the public

recommendations regarding how to dispose of masks, tissues etc
people should only go to recycling centers when strictly necessary
recommendation regarding contacts with sick people at the end of their lifes and of funerals
